author: Amai Ta. Yume
text:
Congratulations on 600k Subscribers. Man, I even forgot how I started to Love Rushi-chi! It hasn't been many months, but every stream Rushi-chi makes, my heart and mind always goes *fuwa fuwa*! Everything that you do is always rewarded and here the viewers, subscribers, members and the fans will surely be there along the way. Please continue to do the best work you do! 

It really hasn't been long, but I'm always craving more on Rushi-chi's stream! Everything really is amazing, fun, interactable with her reactions being cute and even funny! Much love from an overseas bro and that won't change now. I find another reason to keep on moving and hope that I get to live in Japan too someday as I really love the country. It might make it moreso that I could get merchandise more quickly when I live there or when a next live concert and I would want to really join in that concert.

And the stream enduring Trident was tons of fun as well! I'm glad she liked the trident for being cool and awesome! New things for Rushia to discover and I love every single of it!

Nevertheless,  Rushi-chi has been the most endearing and astonishing person I've met! This love that had been spreading to each of one of us. I just wanted to thank you again for the support you made for Rushi-chi to be where she is today. Please continue to support her still, even at bad times and good times. Thank you guys! And thank you Rushi-chi for everything.



Congratulations for the 600k Subscribers. More will come! <3 <3 <3
